devdoc.details: This contract handles cloning aliens and createGen0This contract is split in the following way:      - AlienCore: This provides the methods required for basic non-fungible token

burn(uint256).details: Burns `tokenId`. See {ERC721-_burn}. Requirements: - The caller must own `tokenId` or be an approved operator. emits Event {AlienDestroyed}

params._dadId: The dad of the alien (0 for gen0)
params._generation: The generation number of this alien, must be computed by caller
params._genes: The generic code, must me computed by the caller
params._mumId: The mother of the alien (0 for gen0)
params._owner: The initial owner, must me non-zero Requirements: - msg.sender will pay the creation Fee for creation

getAlien(uint256).details: Returns an alien object based on its ID. Requirements: - The ID must be lower than totalSupply.

getAllAliens(address).details: Returns an array of IDs owned by the address. Requirements: - The ID must be lower than totalSupply.

isApprovedOwner(address,uint256).details: Returns whether `spender` is allowed to manage `tokenId`. Requirements: - `tokenId` must exist.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pauseContract().details: Returns to normal state. Requirements: - The contract must be paused.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transfer(address,address,uint256).details: Assign ownership of a specific alien to an address.This poses no restriction on msg.sender

params._from: The address from who to transfer from, can be 0 for creation of a alien
params._to: The address to who to transfer to, cannot be 0 address
params._tokenId: The id of the transfering alien,

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unpauseContract().details: Returns to normal state. Requirements: - The contract must be paused.

cloneAlien(uint256,uint256).notice: Clone a new alien based on a mom and dad
